<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé hé huá de jīng bīng 迦南336</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé hé huá de jīng bīng gāi shì shén me yàng? yé hé huá de jīng bīng gāi shì shén me yàng?
 yé hé huá de jīng bīng shì léi lì fēng xíng, yé hé huá de jīng bīng shì quán fù jūn zhuāng,
 yé hé huá de jīng bīng zhòu yè shǒu wàng chéng qiáng, yé hé huá de jīng bīng yǒng gǎn qín ná chái láng,
 yé hé huá de jīng bīng shí kè jǐng tì, yé hé huá de jīng bīng xīn xiōng tǎn dàng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>336</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>